Kuwait: IAH Pirbright Molecular Epidemiology Report
---------------------------------------------------
Country and date: Kuwait. 9 Aug 2011
Type: official
Issue: general information

Summary
-------
Number of samples: 2; date collected: 1 Jan 2011; serotype: O;
species: cattle; region sequenced: VP1; topotype: ME-SA;
genotype/strain: PanAsia-2, ANT-10; date sequence last updated: 26 Jul
2011; most related reference strain: O/IRN/88/200 (percentage
identity: 98.12 per cent).

